              ],
              "osterwalder": {
                "relType": "dedicated"
              }
            }
          },
          "rdfs:comment": "Xerox MPS mirrors Michelin Pay-Per-Km: outcome-based service replaces hardware sale. Saves Xerox from bankruptcy (2001). Anne Mulcahy turnaround. Similar to IBM's Gerstner pivot.",
          "sim:sources": [
